	viewer.zoom(2.5);
    viewer.setBackgroundColor('#f9f9f9');

    C1_p_selected: false,

    C2_sp2_selected: false,
    orb_pi_selected: false,
    orb_sigma_selected: false
};

	function toggleFlag(flag) {
		window[flag] = !window[flag];
		updateOrbitals();
	}
	
    $("#C1_p").click(function() { toggleFlag('C1_p_selected');	});
    $("#C2_p").click(function() { toggleFlag('C2_p_selected');	});
    $("#C1_sp2").click(function() { toggleFlag('C1_sp2_selected');	});
    $("#C2_sp2").click(function() { toggleFlag('C2_sp2_selected');	 });
    $("#orb_pi").click(function() { toggleFlag('orb_pi_selected');	 });
    $("#orb_sigma").click(function() { toggleFlag('orb_sigma_selected');  });

	function updateOrbitals() {
		viewer.clear();
		console.log(C1_p_data)
		viewer.addModel(C1_p_data, "cube");
		viewer.setStyle({}, {stick: {radius: 0.15}, sphere: {scale: 0.25}});
		
		

		if (window.C1_p_selected == true) {
			var C1_pVolumeData = new $3Dmol.VolumeData(C1_p_data, "cube");
			viewer.addIsosurface(C1_pVolumeData, {isoval: isovalueOrb, color: "blue", alpha: 0.8, smoothness: 10});
			viewer.addIsosurface(C1_pVolumeData, {isoval: -isovalueOrb, color: "green", alpha: 0.8, smoothness: 10});
		}

		if (window.C2_p_selected == true) {

		}

			viewer.addIsosurface(C1_sp2_pVolumeData, {isoval: isovalueOrb, color: "blue", alpha: 0.8, smoothness: 10});
			viewer.addIsosurface(C1_sp2_pVolumeData, {isoval: -isovalueOrb, color: "green", alpha: 0.8, smoothness: 10});
		}

			viewer.addIsosurface(C2_sp2_pVolumeData, {isoval: isovalueOrb, color: "blue", alpha: 0.8, smoothness: 10});
			viewer.addIsosurface(C2_sp2_pVolumeData, {isoval: -isovalueOrb, color: "green", alpha: 0.8, smoothness: 10});
		}

			viewer.addIsosurface(orb_pi_pVolumeData, {isoval: isovalueOrb, color: "blue", alpha: 0.8, smoothness: 10});
